HEADWORD: Zincification
<hw>Zinc`i*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
process of applying zinc; the condition of being zincified, or covered
with zinc; galvanization.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zincify</ent>⟦br⟧
